data.description: Silent country living, but minutes away from the Walmart shopping center, Olympic College, Bangor Naval Base, Highway 3 and the heart of beautiful downtown Poulsbo!  Lovely private setting on almost an acre and a half.  Main floor includes cozy kitchen, eat in area as well as a rec room and formal dining and living rooms and a bedroom/ office. Upstairs you will find double doors opening into the large primary bedroom and En suite bath equipped with soaking tub and separate shower, and a walk in closet!  Two other bedrooms and a bathroom are situated up stairs plus a very large bonus room for office, exercise, living or whatever your living needs may be.  New garage door, and insulation in crawl space and attic.
